ygData.subject: Re: 16th level water song
ygData.msgSnippet: Let me answer this question in a non-spoiler free way. For a fun excursion, go take a look at Kedge Keep, a dungeon completely underwater in Dagnor s Cauldron.
ygData.messageBody:
Let me answer this question in a non-spoiler free way.

For a fun excursion, go take a look at Kedge Keep, a dungeon completely
underwater in Dagnor's Cauldron. Very high level place, way beyond me (35 -
50 is what I have heard). I am guessing that one day most of us will find
ourselves in a group going to Kedge Keep, where our only mission is to stay
out of trouble and sing that water breathing song.

Of course, I've never really been there, so I may be wrong . . .

-Musil
